     F********************************************* JYUR55 **
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           I@SEC  100
     C                     PARM           O@HOUR  40
     C                     PARM           O@MIN   20
     C                     PARM           O@SEC   20
      *
     C           I@SEC     DIV  60        W@MIN  100
     C                     MVR            O@SEC
      *
     C           W@MIN     DIV  60        W@HOUR 100
     C                     MVR            O@MIN
      *
     C                     Z-ADDW@HOUR    O@HOUR
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
